OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784220475
OL,3,CEngland star helps marathon hero
OL,4,Cfacing terminal dementia get World Cup
OL,5,Ctickets
OL,7,FA fundraising hero facing a terminal
OL,8,Fdementia diagnosis has been invited to
OL,9,Fthe World Cup semi-final by England
OL,10,Fmidfielder Kobbie Mainoo.
OL,12,FJordan Adams, one half of the FTD
OL,13,FBrothers, who have raised nearly #2
OL,14,Fmillion for Alzheimer's charities,
OL,15,Fposted a video on social media from a
OL,16,Fflight to Atlanta, saying it was his
OL,17,Fdream to watch England play in the
OL,18,Fsemi-final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
