FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784220475
OL,3,CEngland star helps marathon hero
OL,4,Cfacing terminal dementia get World Cup
OL,5,Ctickets
OL,7,FTo his surprise, less than 15 hours
OL,8,Flater, that dream became a reality.
OL,9,FMainoo had reached out and offered him
OL,10,Fa ticket to the game.
OL,12,FIn a message shared by Jordan, the
OL,13,FManchester United midfielder wrote:
OL,14,F"Hey bro, hope you're good! Please can
OL,15,Fyou send me the email linked to your
OL,16,FFIFA ticket app and I'll get a ticket
OL,17,Fsent over to you."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
