PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784220475
OL,3,CEngland star helps marathon hero
OL,4,Cfacing terminal dementia get World Cup
OL,5,Ctickets
OL,7,FThe brothers both carry a rare
OL,8,Finherited gene mutation linked to FTD,
OL,9,Fmeaning they could also develop the
OL,10,Fcondition in their 40s.
OL,12,FFollowing his diagnosis in 2018,
OL,13,FJordan decided to run against time and
OL,14,Fcompleted 33 marathons in 33 days for
OL,15,Fcharity, alongside his brother.
OL,17,FThis included Jordan running the
OL,18,FLondon Marathon with a fridge on his
OL,19,Fback to represent the weight carried
OL,20,Fby those with a dementia diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
